\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 YOU WERE MADE TO WORSHIP\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs28 \cf0 \

\f0\b WHY
\f1\b0  can't we just change behaviors? This may be the point where some of you are tempted to checkout but please stick with me for a second. 
\f0\b You were made to worship
\f1\b0 . You were created by an All-Powerful God who designed you in such a way that you will worship something or someone whether you want to or not.\
\
Don't believe me? I get it...this is a stretch for some but let me try to explain.\
\
Have you ever seen someone who Monday through Friday appear to be very normal acting mature adults. Only to transition into a crazed fan who paint their face, memorize chants, and scream at the top of their lungs at a tv while watching other grown men and women play a game. From the outside it seems crazy but to that person, it's what they love, it's what they do, it's who they are. They're a fan and they're not ashamed of it. Whether they know it or not, they are worshiping at the alter of the NCAA, NFL, MLB, NBA, or even their kids soccer game sometimes.\
\
And when I say someone, who I mean is me. I'm the crazed fan who yells at the tv at the top of his lungs so loudly that I've had a hard time preaching the next day because I lost my voice. I'm the person who has had their night ruined because a group of well meaning college players lost a game hundreds of miles away from me. I'm the one who says weird things like "We lost tonight or We won tonight" even though I've never played college football or attended the great university of Notre Dame. I say 'we' because I feel connected, I feel a part of it, I want to be associated and tied to it. Someone, it me.\
\
And someone is you too. You worship all the time without realizing it. There's a good chance you may not care about how Notre Dame plays in a random college football game. But you worship something. There is something all of us have in our lives that drives us.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
