\f0\b all your heart
\f1\b0  and with 
\f0\b all your soul
\f1\b0  and with 
\f0\b all your mind
\f1\b0  and with 
\f0\b all your strength
\f1\b0 .\'92 \cf0 \
\pard\tx560\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
If that isn't a definition of worship then I don't know what is. Jesus says that our hearts, souls, minds, and strength should all be put into worship God. If this is done then the rest of the commands that we struggle with all fall into place.\
\
Essentially what Jesus is doing is separating the symptoms from the disease. The thing that has your heart is what you are tempted to worship. The thing you think about constantly is what you are tempted to worship. Where you put your energy and strength is what you may be tempted to worship. \
\
For Jesus, if you get worship right, the rest will fall into place. And to get worship right, you should worship The Lord God.\
\
